Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.60,0:00:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面我是望月
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我是森
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.11,0:00:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這個房子很古老
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,住了很久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.30,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,工廠在仙台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人要去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.15,0:00:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,加上夫人的話27人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-結衣是嗎 -你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.51,0:01:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-我認識她很奇怪嗎\N-不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-夫人是專務 -很多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-原來如此那麼走吧 -請進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.70,0:01:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是森
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.02,0:02:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(在老公遺照前被侵犯)\N(我快要瘋狂JUY507)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎 我不知道你們認識
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,給你添麻煩了對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,的事情請你節哀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我和他是同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣是後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,以前三個人經常一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,大學畢業後他繼承父業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,然後過了十年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,某個會議的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.70,0:03:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他們結婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,說到底還是被他搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.60,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候我們都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他想讓我幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣也需要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是世界上發生什麼事\N誰也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-發生這樣的事情-那麼結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起你了 也不能這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.60,0:04:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,工廠的欠款事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,欠款的事情等會說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,現在是夫人很失落的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.60,0:04:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候回去更好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,改日我再來 那麼失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.80,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真的讓你傷心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快點好起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,再繼續聊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.50,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.39,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我會陪著你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣討厭我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.89,0:06:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,下次見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.24,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,(社長室)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.30,0:07:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶她來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你先離開下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我想兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,請你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,前幾天是我很慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.40,0:07:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,借我們那麼多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以保住工廠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起頭 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.80,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-社員也會沒工作 -冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了 森
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-我什麼都做 所以\N-我不會濫用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.10,0:08:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你先冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.70,0:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的嗎 -我個人來負責
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是結衣也要一起走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不勉強你 你考慮下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-什麼意思 -總之
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你想好好考慮下\N心情好點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,等你想好了回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老公
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,前幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我很過分失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,這沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以救我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.10,0:12:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老公面前不行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,做好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-別這樣啊 -不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-現在就要說 -我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.30,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-那麼我走了 -等下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-真的可以拯救公司嗎\N-當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.40,0:13:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不是交給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣更快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快點做出決斷好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-不放開我 放開我\N-可能不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到你的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-就忍不住了\N-住手 放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都想得到你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.20,0:15:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有這種機會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.40,0:15:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.90,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我什麼都幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.89,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,非常喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和以前一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:16:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.90,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.81,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很軟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,手也軟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,早就想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,非常可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真下流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你也想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.26,0:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是的 -喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.00,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在他面前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和我做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,非常下流哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,知道自己的表情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-給他看看 -不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.98,0:21:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.10,0:21:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讓他看看你的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.70,0:21:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.90,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.50,0:22:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-住手 -你不管公司了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,-老實點 -不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.20,0:23:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,手拿開
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不管公司了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.20,0:24:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.80,0:24:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.40,0:24:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,公司
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,還有員工的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.50,0:24:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都看你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.60,0:25:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒好軟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.90,0:25:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.20,0:25:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.90,0:25:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你也舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.10,0:26:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.66,0:26:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.40,0:26:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,變熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.00,0:27:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.09,0:27:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.40,0:27:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.70,0:27:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,勃起了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.00,0:27:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看到結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.40,0:27:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我就受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.60,0:27:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道嗎 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.59,0:27:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一直一直
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.70,0:27:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我都想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.60,0:27:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.90,0:27:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.20,0:28:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我要脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.73,0:28:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.51,0:28:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.50,0:28:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡你才勃起的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.20,0:28:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.80,0:28:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,傳達我的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.90,0:29:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.80,0:29:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,用力用力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.40,0:29:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,變硬了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.30,0:29:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼不看我
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.60,0:29:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-你幹嘛 -看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.90,0:30:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很好的看著
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.20,0:30:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,放開我放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.00,0:30:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.82,0:30:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.80,0:31:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.30,0:31:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近點看看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.60,0:31:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我不看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.00,0:31:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.50,0:32:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.90,0:32:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續 結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.90,0:32:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,興奮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.00,0:32:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.40,0:33:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股翹起來
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.40,0:33:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,像狗一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.70,0:33:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.20,0:33:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,動起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.20,0:33:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,-快點 -不行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.70,0:33:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不是什麼都做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.90,0:33:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.90,0:33:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.50,0:33:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,也可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.09,0:34:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以接受我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.30,0:35:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很軟 很舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.50,0:35:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股也舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.90,0:35:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很軟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.80,0:35:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.50,0:35:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣的熱度
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.20,0:35:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我感受到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.50,0:35:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.60,0:36:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,非常美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.90,0:36:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好看
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.50,0:36:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,粉色的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.80,0:37:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.09,0:37:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.19,0:37:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,發抖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.30,0:37:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.40,0:37:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.80,0:38:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.00,0:38:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.20,0:38:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,身體很誠實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.00,0:38:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.09,0:38:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好多水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.59,0:38:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,準備好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.90,0:39:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.91,0:39:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害吸進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.70,0:39:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.70,0:39:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.30,0:39:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就想了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.09,0:40:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.90,0:40:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公比誰舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.20,0:40:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我來動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.24,0:41:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.40,0:41:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很下流哦結衣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.29,0:42:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.60,0:42:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的 在老公面前
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.60,0:42:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,會興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.80,0:43:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.40,0:43:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.13,0:43:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.09,0:43:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.10,0:43:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.58,0:45:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,發抖了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.20,0:47:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.10,0:47:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了要射了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.60,0:48:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.60,0:48:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,舔乾淨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.00,0:49:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好像
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.80,0:49:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,有點做多了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.20,0:49:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我太喜歡你了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.40,0:49:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,今天謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.00,0:49:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.60,0:51:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,(居喪期間)
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.24,0:51:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,(居喪期間)
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.15,0:52:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.62,0:52:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣才會興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.09,0:52:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-對吧 -你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.10,0:52:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.01,0:52:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,-你都濕了 -住手
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.14,0:52:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.24,0:53:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.47,0:53:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 快點住手
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.80,0:53:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.80,0:54:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.90,0:54:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,很麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.20,0:54:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,社長也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.80,0:54:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.19,0:54:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,公司怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.60,0:55:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,其實
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.50,0:55:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,會幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.50,0:55:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.50,0:55:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,正式發表要過幾天
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.00,0:55:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.19,0:55:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.19,0:55:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,繼續工作就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.90,0:55:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,專務同意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.90,0:55:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.10,0:55:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.40,0:55:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,手機響了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.30,0:55:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是的 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.24,0:55:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-興奮了吧 -沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.61,0:56:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.21,0:57:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,身體發熱了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.25,0:57:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.63,0:57:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜歡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.48,0:57:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.55,0:57:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.74,0:57:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,發出聲音會暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.95,0:58:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼好多水
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.86,0:58:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.76,0:58:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-還沒進去吧 -住手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.92,0:59:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,濕了濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.93,0:59:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.41,0:59:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,-舒服嗎 -不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.87,0:59:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,-住手 -但是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.30,1:00:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你都興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.04,1:00:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.64,1:01:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴這裡都濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.57,1:01:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,拔出來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.29,1:02:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-沒暴露吧 -住手
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.42,1:02:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好多水
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.02,1:02:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼騷啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.49,1:02:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,下流的味道 你試試
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.94,1:02:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,有人在會興奮吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.07,1:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是的 -那麼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.24,1:02:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.47,1:03:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼濕了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.40,1:03:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很熱
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.26,1:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣會舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.01,1:04:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,這麼多水
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.70,1:05:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.60,1:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,專務說了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.30,1:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,公司正常進行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.00,1:06:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,誰當社長
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.30,1:06:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我先運營公司
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.00,1:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,專務呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.60,1:06:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.30,1:06:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,專務
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.30,1:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,做經理
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.30,1:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,所以大家放心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.80,1:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,工資
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.90,1:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.99,1:06:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,-當然了 -太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.63,1:06:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-很棒的姿勢 -彷彿
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.09,1:06:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,像是做不完的夢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.70,1:07:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,森每天都侵犯我\N我想快點結束
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.80,1:07:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我在心裡嘶吼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.19,1:07:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,老實點
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.90,1:07:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-聽我的話 -但是
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.00,1:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那種夢沒想到我會這樣
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.40,1:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,很好哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.69,1:12:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 腿張開給他看看
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.49,1:13:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很好讓他看看
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.69,1:15:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.45,1:15:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我的人了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.60,1:15:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,結束後
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.60,1:15:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.80,1:15:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,和我重新生活吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.45,1:15:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,看你老公
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.40,1:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,做最後的告白吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.51,1:17:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,手也好吃哦 結衣
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.00,1:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我的也試試吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.09,1:19:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.10,1:19:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.00,1:20:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,再硬一點吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.65,1:21:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,摩擦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.00,1:22:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害的摩擦
Dialogue: 0,1:22:28.90,1:22:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,更硬了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.89,1:23:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,用力親我
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.19,1:23:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.10,1:24:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.90,1:25:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.90,1:25:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我都勃起了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.04,1:26:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.59,1:26:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股也給我看看
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.50,1:29:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,腿張開看看
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.40,1:31:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.22,1:32:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
